      ...Algunas personas que trabajaron conmigo
    </p>
  </div>

  <article class="grid xl:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mx-auto xl:mt-20">
    <Card>
      <BiceVida class="w-32" />
      <p class="mt-2 text-blue-deep">
        "Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur. Tortor imperdiet suspendisse
        nec a eleifend. Vel aliquam quis ac sit sit imperdiet. Lectus mattis
        feugiat habitant metus fusce scelerisque iaculis condimentum orci. Vel
        hac ut tortor sed tortor tempor et."
      </p>
    </Card>
    <Card
      class="p-5 bg-white border border-orange-light rounded-lg shadow-lg max-w-[352px]"
    >
      <BiceVida class="w-32" />
      <p class="mt-2 text-blue-deep">
        "Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur. Tortor imperdiet suspendisse
